- If requested by the Licensor, you must retain any attributions accompanying the Licensed Material
- You may not claim or imply that the Licensor endorses your use without their permission

b. **NonCommercial**. You may not use the Licensed Material for Commercial Purposes.

c. **ShareAlike**. You may offer or imposeAdapted Material terms and conditions on Adapted Material you make, fork, or create based on the Licensed Material, provided that:
- Your Adapted Material carries prominent notices stating that you changed the Licensed Material
- Your Adapted Material carries notices stating that it is available under this license
- You must include the text of, or the URL or hyperlink to, this license
- If You Create an Adapted Material, You may not offer or impose any additional or different terms or conditions on, or apply, any Effective Technological Measures on, Adapted Material that restrict exercise of rights granted under the license

